@startuml
participant "FDA S3 Bucket" as FDA
participant "Raw S3 Bucket" as Raw
participant "Landing S3 Bucket" as Landing
participant "Curated S3 Bucket" as Curated
participant "EMR (Spark)" as EMR
participant "AWS Glue" as Glue
participant "AWS Athena" as Athena
participant "Step Functions" as StepFunctions
participant "Lambda" as Lambda
participant "Comprehend Medical" as ComprehendMedical

FDA -> Raw: Ingest FDA drug label data
Raw -> EMR: Read raw data
EMR -> EMR: Deflate zipped files
EMR -> EMR: Explode JSON arrays
EMR -> Landing: Write transformed data
Landing -> EMR: Read landed data
EMR -> EMR: Convert data types
EMR -> EMR: Partition data
EMR -> Curated: Write curated data
Curated -> Glue: Crawl and catalog data
Glue -> Athena: Update metadata

StepFunctions -> Lambda: Trigger configure_count
Lambda -> Lambda: Set up processing counts
StepFunctions -> Lambda: Trigger query_athena
Lambda -> Athena: Query drug indications
Athena --> Lambda: Return query results
StepFunctions -> Lambda: Trigger call_comprehend
Lambda -> ComprehendMedical: Extract medical entities
ComprehendMedical --> Lambda: Return extracted entities
Lambda -> Curated: Store extracted indications
StepFunctions -> Lambda: Trigger iterator
Lambda -> StepFunctions: Determine if more processing needed

EMR -> Curated: Read FDA product data
EMR -> Curated: Read extracted indications
EMR -> EMR: Combine FDA data with indications
EMR -> Curated: Write final curated data
@enduml